      • add

        public T add(T newEntry)
        Description copied from interface: SearchTreeInterface
        Adds a new entry to this tree, if if does not match an existing object in the tree. Ohterwise, replaces the existing object with the new entry.
        Specified by:
        add in interface SearchTreeInterface<T extends java.lang.Comparable<? super T>>
        Parameters:
        newEntry - An object to be added to the tree.
        Returns:
